{"tid":2504770,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣新生活 2","createTime":"2021-04-26T06:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:30:43.000Z","uid":190135,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f94eacb1faf4904fc3f316660d435f9ea5fa5351","tid":2504770,"uid":190135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"今日同大家介紹下響台灣嘅娛樂<br />\n<br />\n1.睇戲<br />\n台灣睇戲除咗有一般戲院仲有二輪放映嘅電影院<br />\n<br />\n一般台灣人睇戲多數都係去西門町 <br />\n西門町嘅戲院好多 <br />\n價錢比較平 大約300台幣左右<br />\n有d戲院大嘅House 超級大 好似大會堂咁 <br />\n台灣亦有d戲院開係商場入面 我就去過板橋大遠百果間<br />\n票價通常就貴d 400台幣up<br />\nBtw呢期嘅電影都冇咩好睇 我覺得King Kong戰哥斯拉、永生戰同真人快打都唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二輪放映電影院叫U2~適合d情侶去？<br />\n可以去睇已經落畫嘅電影 <br />\n我個人冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.唱K<br />\n台灣KTV有幾間大公司 <br />\n分別叫做星聚點 錢櫃 好樂迪<br />\n聽講錢櫃廣東話歌會多d 不過我就冇去過<br />\n星聚點有座地嘅Mic 環境算幾好 嘢食都幾好食<br />\n好樂迪就好似最多分店 周圍都見到<br />\n<br />\n除咗呢d大公司<br />\n仲有一d細間嘅 有間叫做星光大道 <br />\n呢類型嘅KTV 環境、音響會差d <br />\n不過你想搵咩歌都應該會有 因為佢好似冇買版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外響某d商場/街邊都會有d好似電話亭嘅KTV machine <br />\n入錢就可以開始唱 唱一首歌都得 <br />\n呢d電話亭都有唔少廣東話歌<br />\n<br />\n3.遊戲館E7<br />\nE7係一間集合不同遊樂設施嘅遊戲館 <br />\n有d似進階版機鋪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由氣塾球、太鼓、打異形機、KTV電話亭、飛標到保齡球都有 <br />\n買一張門票就可以玩哂所有野<br />\n門票有分假日和平日、5小時/3小時 <br />\n大約都係二百幾台幣左右 一d都唔貴"},{"pid":"385cf9e8ed1b9bbe82b21ef07985159a05492603","tid":2504770,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:29:45.000Z","msg":"台北最好既娛樂係沿住河堤踩ubike<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a0314091db122dc0cbafee447eb2c715b6a062","tid":2504770,"uid":190135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"385cf9e8ed1b9bbe82b21ef07985159a05492603","tid":2504770,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:29:45.000Z","msg":"台北最好既娛樂係沿住河堤踩ubike<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"總有落雨嘅時候 唯有搵d室內嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa09340c529ad5211da154d5bc9113e1bb4c9851","tid":2504770,"uid":383535,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:36:07.000Z","msg":"盡快報樓主，就係呢d人玩爛個制度，搞到台灣收緊移民"},{"pid":"9dd577d9c3f9f5b24e7ba51b546026a333c016df","tid":2504770,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我在台灣的一年移民監<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n移民台灣門檻｜今年內取消一年居留可定居入籍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8021922f7088bba1a1ed34d607c75a295681cb08","tid":2504770,"uid":190135,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9dd577d9c3f9f5b24e7ba51b546026a333c016df","tid":2504770,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我在台灣的一年移民監<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n移民台灣門檻｜今年內取消一年居留可定居入籍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"4d2443aee72de7f7d9019a96099ea34149f802d3","tid":2504770,"uid":82267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"收皮喇"},